<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1451136>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Metaporcelaimus concinnus sp. n. A: Anterior region in lateral, median view. B: Lip region in lateral, surface view. C: Pharyngo-intestinal junction. D: Female, posterior genital branch. E: Male, posterior body region. F: Vagina. G: Male, caudal region and spicule. H: Female, caudal region. I: Pars dilatata oviductus-uterus junction." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1451136/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1451138>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Metaporcelaimus concinnus sp. n. (LM). A: Lip region in lateral, surface view. B: Anterior region in lateral, median view. C: Pharyngo-intestinal junction. D: Vagina. E, F: Vulva in ventral view. G: Pars dilatata oviductus-uterus junction. H: Female, caudal region; I: Male, caudal region and spicule. (Scale bars = 10 µm.)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1451138/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

